1
00:00:05,228 --> 00:00:08,519
Once I was speaking like that
to Guru Mahārāj, and he went,

2
00:00:08,519 --> 00:00:10,158
“Deep thinker.”

3
00:00:10,643 --> 00:00:14,209
[Not What You Know but Who You Know]

4
00:00:14,344 --> 00:00:16,356
“He’s a deep thinker,”
this that and the other,

5
00:00:16,356 --> 00:00:19,809
“and what’s more, 
he likes me.”

6
00:00:20,779 --> 00:00:24,491
But if you just like him,
it’s okay;

7
00:00:24,491 --> 00:00:28,601
you don’t have to be a deep thinker
if you just like.

8
00:00:28,782 --> 00:00:32,953
In the spiritual circles 
it’s not what you know;

9
00:00:32,953 --> 00:00:37,777
it’s who you know and who you serve—
thank the Lord.

